```plantuml
@startuml exmgr_GatewayXM

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<IoT>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Cloud>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<Gateway>> LightYellow
}

rectangle "IoT Devices" as iot <<IoT>> {
  [ModBus Smart Meters]
  [ESP8266/ESP32 Sensor Nodes]
}

rectangle "GatewayXM" as gateway <<Gateway>> {
  [Eclipse Kura]
  [Artemis MQTT Broker]
  [Kura-Tb Bundle]
  [Docker Container]
}

rectangle "Cloud Services" as cloud <<Cloud>> {
  [Thingsboard IoT Platform]
  [Resin.io (Balena)]
}

[ModBus Smart Meters] --> [Eclipse Kura] : Data
[ESP8266/ESP32 Sensor Nodes] --> [Artemis MQTT Broker] : Telemetry Data
[Artemis MQTT Broker] --> [Kura-Tb Bundle] : Forward Data
[Eclipse Kura] --> [Kura-Tb Bundle] : Asset Data
[Kura-Tb Bundle] --> [Thingsboard IoT Platform] : Forward Data
[Resin.io (Balena)] --> [Docker Container] : Manage & Update
[Docker Container] --> [Eclipse Kura] : Host
[Docker Container] --> [Artemis MQTT Broker] : Host
[Docker Container] --> [Kura-Tb Bundle] : Host

note right of [ESP8266/ESP32 Sensor Nodes]
  Forms mesh network
  Supports OTA updates
end note

note right of [Eclipse Kura]
  Modular OSGi framework
  Extensible components
end note

note right of [Resin.io (Balena)]
  Manages OTA updates
  for gateway
end note

@enduml
